                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / So hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l9">Ott <expan>Grefemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> auch
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> fürbraht vvie Jm
